ygData.subject: FBR/ROO
ygData.msgSnippet: Hi there, i will post some info about najena for those interested. Every 18 min, the room will either spawn a single fire elemental or najena with 2 magicians.
ygData.messageBody:
Hi there, i will post some info about najena for those interested. Every 18 min, the room will either
spawn a single fire elemental or najena with 2 magicians. If your unlucky, Najena may not spawn for a few hours
straight. Najena is lvl 29 and the 2 magicians r lvl 24-25. She either drops a FBR(99.99% of the time) or the black
book with silver runes( 0.01% of the time).

On ROO, the oracle is lvl 34 and she has a lvl 42 paladin guard ( hes a pain in the ass ).

Hope that helps.
